# ENTITY::SET_ENTITY_CAN_ONLY_BE_DAMAGED_BY_ENTITY

## Parameters
* **ENTITY_INDEX** entity
* **ENTITY_INDEX** damagingEntity

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Sets an entity to only be damaged by one other entity
